## Quick Start

### Backend

```bash
cd backend
uv sync
uv run python init_data.py
uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port {{ backend_port }}
```

### Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Combined

```bash
./start.sh
```

