- sysadmin / 123456 (system admin)
- manager / 123456 (manager)

## Architecture

This project follows a three-layer architecture:

1. **`core/`** — Domain-agnostic Ontology Runtime framework
2. **`app/{{ domain_name }}/`** — {{ domain_display_name }} business domain (pluggable)
3. **`app/system/`** — System management (RBAC, menus, config, etc.)

